{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/SteamDescriptionTitle1.png?t=1740587077\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelike Action Shooter\u00a0 +\u00a0 Turn-based Card Deckbuilder</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/Rogue-Drone-Hunter_Action.gif?t=1740587077\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rogue Drone Hunter</strong> is a unique action roguelike, merging deckbuilding with real-time combat.\u00a0 Explore the dangerous outskirts of Elysia to collect powerful cards and game-changing perks in your fight to defend humanity against dangerous machines.\u00a0 Team up with your drone companion to uncover the mysterious origins of the rogue drone threat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/Rogue-Drone-Hunter_Deck.gif?t=1740587077\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Diverse Deckbuilding</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft your ultimate deck from hundreds of unique cards and create powerful synergies to obliterate your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/Rogue-Drone-Hunter_Build.gif?t=1740587077\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>Real-Time Action Shooter</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in intense shooting bullet-hell combat, while dodging attacks and taking down relentless boss machines and enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Roguelike Replayability</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover new surprises as you venture beyond Elysia.\u00a0 Face a variety of cards, perks, and enemies that challenge your skills and ensure every run feels unique.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>Befriend Unique Characters</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage with diverse personalities through compelling conversations, and uncover the secrets of Elysia and the mysterious fog that surrounds the city.\u00a0 Will you be able to rally humanity to stand against the escalating machine threat?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/Rogue-Drone-Hunter_Friends.gif?t=1740587077\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>Tactical Terrain</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience fully destructible terrain and objects.\u00a0 Take cover in bushes or demolish structures to gain the advantage. Surprise your foes by setting off explosive traps and turning the battlefield to your favor.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3331400?t=1740587077","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/0b3ca8de910e01d39131dad259b31c368988a276/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740587077","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/3c4129e25b3387483225e43055cac8803fbd3035/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740587077","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/3c4129e25b3387483225e43055cac8803fbd3035/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740587077","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331400/extras/SteamDescriptionTitle1.png?t=1740587077\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelike Action Shooter\u00a0 +\u00a0 Turn-based Card Deckbuilder</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=